But I don't know the exact situation
on your end either,

00:25:15.100 --> 00:25:16.340
so I can only tell Mom

00:25:16.460 --> 00:25:17.790
that you're doing fine.

00:25:19.020 --> 00:25:19.890
But...

00:25:20.720 --> 00:25:21.930
are you really okay?

00:25:23.110 --> 00:25:25.110
Once things are settled on your end,

00:25:25.270 --> 00:25:26.930
you'll come see me, won't you?

00:25:34.360 --> 00:25:36.200
From your voice, you seem like...

00:25:36.200 --> 00:25:37.800
you're still not doing well.

00:25:40.400 --> 00:25:41.730
I'm still alive for now.

00:25:41.810 --> 00:25:43.410
I'd like to recommend someone to you.

00:25:43.410 --> 00:25:44.330
Dr. Julia.

00:25:44.590 --> 00:25:46.040
She's a good friend of mine

00:25:46.040 --> 00:25:48.370
and an excellent rehabilitation doctor.

00:25:49.150 --> 00:25:50.430
She'll definitely be of help to you.

00:25:50.430 --> 00:25:51.560
She'll be here soon.

00:26:05.520 --> 00:26:06.190
Hello,

00:26:06.720 --> 00:26:07.650
I'm Julia.

00:26:08.130 --> 00:26:10.090
Lin Sui should have told you about me.

00:26:10.090 --> 00:26:12.310
He specifically invited me back
from Canada.

00:26:12.310 --> 00:26:14.710
The upcoming rehabilitation
will be very tough,

00:26:14.710 --> 00:26:15.630
but believe me,

00:26:16.030 --> 00:26:17.630
it will definitely help you.

00:26:25.080 --> 00:26:25.880
Hold it there.

00:26:30.570 --> 00:26:32.100
Try to control it yourself.

00:26:33.240 --> 00:26:34.240
Relax.

00:26:36.100 --> 00:26:37.170
Don't fight me.

00:26:37.960 --> 00:26:38.600
Yes.

00:26:38.860 --> 00:26:40.260
Push harder. Control it.

00:26:43.650 --> 00:26:44.480
Great!

00:26:44.930 --> 00:26:46.170
In the early stages, we'll work through

00:26:46.170 --> 00:26:47.900
hip and knee flexion exercises

00:26:48.000 --> 00:26:50.610
to train your joint mobility and strength.

00:26:52.070 --> 00:26:53.350
Now, try it yourself.

00:26:53.610 --> 00:26:54.410
Bend.

00:27:18.600 --> 00:27:19.250
Zhao,

00:27:19.410 --> 00:27:21.650
I've gradually adapted to life here

00:27:21.850 --> 00:27:23.090
and made new friends.

00:27:23.510 --> 00:27:24.220
Also,

00:27:24.420 --> 00:27:25.730
all those difficult technical terms

00:27:25.730 --> 00:27:27.580
our professors use in class,

00:27:27.740 --> 00:27:29.400
I can understand them all now.

00:27:29.930 --> 00:27:30.650
Zhao,

00:27:31.060 --> 00:27:32.520
how are things over there?

00:27:33.330 --> 00:27:34.440
In terms of surgery,

00:27:34.440 --> 00:27:36.240
we've done all we can.

00:27:36.410 --> 00:27:39.090
The rest depends mainly on rehabilitation.

00:27:39.290 --> 00:27:40.090
I understand.

00:27:41.480 --> 00:27:42.280
Doctor,

00:27:44.810 --> 00:27:46.410
will he be able to race again?

00:27:46.610 --> 00:27:47.520
Racing?

00:27:48.170 --> 00:27:49.190
Being able to stand

00:27:49.190 --> 00:27:51.440
and live without a wheelchair
would be fortunate enough.

00:27:51.440 --> 00:27:52.640
Forget about racing.

00:27:53.240 --> 00:27:53.890
Sir,

00:27:54.060 --> 00:27:56.120
your spinal nerves have been injured

00:27:56.340 --> 00:27:58.340
and you have multiple tendon tears.

00:27:58.370 --> 00:27:59.440
The rehabilitation process

00:27:59.440 --> 00:28:00.700
will be extremely long and painful.

00:28:00.700 --> 00:28:02.430
You must be mentally prepared.

00:28:05.170 --> 00:28:06.040
Thank you.

00:28:06.240 --> 00:28:07.240
Let me see you out.

00:28:08.620 --> 00:28:10.510
Contact me if you need anything.

00:28:31.280 --> 00:28:32.810
Jiang Mu sent you a message?

00:28:35.030 --> 00:28:38.760
She's been messaging you a lot
these past three months, hasn't she?

00:28:41.660 --> 00:28:44.390
You didn't leave all of them unanswered,
did you?

00:28:45.440 --> 00:28:46.840
In my current condition,

00:28:48.600 --> 00:28:50.530
how am I supposed to respond to her?

00:28:52.480 --> 00:28:53.890
Should I tell her,

00:28:57.300 --> 00:28:58.130
"Mu,

00:29:00.070 --> 00:29:02.470
I'll most likely be disabled
in the future,

00:29:05.250 --> 00:29:06.510
either using crutches

00:29:07.280 --> 00:29:08.340
or in a wheelchair.

00:29:10.210 --> 00:29:12.140
Would you still want to be with me?"

00:29:14.330 --> 00:29:15.480
Jiang Mu would be willing.

00:29:15.480 --> 00:29:16.480
But I'm not.

00:29:22.130 --> 00:29:24.200
She deserves a better life.

00:29:27.330 --> 00:29:29.330
Besides, the case isn't closed yet.

00:29:32.980 --> 00:29:33.740
Sanlai,

00:29:35.940 --> 00:29:37.400
don't contact her either.

00:29:40.080 --> 00:29:40.910
We...

00:29:50.300 --> 00:29:51.460
We should all try

00:29:53.960 --> 00:29:55.610
to give her a peaceful life.

00:31:11.160 --> 00:31:12.440
I'm right here.

00:31:12.680 --> 00:31:15.080
You don't need
to be yearning day and night.

00:31:17.370 --> 00:31:18.630
I want to clear my name.

00:31:19.680 --> 00:31:21.210
Especially after you came.

00:31:22.710 --> 00:31:24.080
I want this proof of innocence even more.

00:31:23.010 --> 00:31:29.410
♪ Perhaps the weather's damp and mild ♪

00:31:25.520 --> 00:31:26.890
I want to prove myself.

00:31:28.790 --> 00:31:29.590
At the very least,

00:31:29.430 --> 00:31:33.260
♪ Perhaps it's about the habit
of bearing ♪

00:31:30.630 --> 00:31:31.670
I deserve you.

