Even just an emoji would be fine.

00:32:25.890 --> 00:32:28.570
Why won't you respond to me?

00:32:27.110 --> 00:32:33.250
♪ Brave enough to be sure is my instinct ♪

00:32:33.280 --> 00:32:38.390
♪ I believe
maybe it just takes a little resolve ♪

00:32:38.660 --> 00:32:42.000
♪ To turn wishes into shooting stars ♪

00:32:42.430 --> 00:32:47.200
♪ Mirroring the eyes that gaze at me ♪

00:32:53.180 --> 00:33:00.070
♪ Crossing the path,
stepping into your life ♪

00:33:08.340 --> 00:33:09.670
Are you feeling better?

00:33:13.370 --> 00:33:15.230
This sort of pain will come again.

00:33:15.890 --> 00:33:17.150
Some of it is physical.

00:33:17.260 --> 00:33:19.680
Some of it are triggered by
traumatic memories.

00:33:19.680 --> 00:33:21.040
But mostly,

00:33:21.200 --> 00:33:23.440
it's psychological and
physical pain intertwined.

00:33:23.440 --> 00:33:24.170
So,

00:33:25.000 --> 00:33:25.850
don't worry.

00:33:26.090 --> 00:33:27.000
I'll help you.

00:33:30.240 --> 00:33:30.960
Just relax.

00:33:31.240 --> 00:33:32.240
I'll go get busy now.

00:33:32.240 --> 00:33:33.840
Call me if you need anything.

00:33:38.790 --> 00:33:40.720
Lift your feet up. Don't drag them.

00:33:43.180 --> 00:33:44.580
Each step can be smaller,

00:33:45.020 --> 00:33:46.220
but keep them steady.

00:33:50.810 --> 00:33:51.730
Relax your upper body.

00:33:51.730 --> 00:33:54.260
Try to use the strength
from your lower limbs.

00:34:00.070 --> 00:34:01.310
Good. Go slower.

00:34:04.520 --> 00:34:05.150
Yes.

00:34:06.390 --> 00:34:07.280
Lift your foot.

00:34:14.570 --> 00:34:15.340
Very good.

00:34:20.179 --> 00:34:20.820
Good.

00:34:26.880 --> 00:34:27.810
Talented people

00:34:27.860 --> 00:34:29.860
tend to bounce back pretty quickly.

00:34:32.730 --> 00:34:34.190
Let's stop here for today.

00:34:36.480 --> 00:34:37.120
Thank you.

00:34:40.440 --> 00:34:41.370
Have some water.

00:34:49.080 --> 00:34:50.409
I have good news for you.

00:34:52.080 --> 00:34:53.480
The case has been solved.

00:34:57.560 --> 00:34:58.250
Really?

00:34:59.080 --> 00:35:00.940
The amount involved is enormous.

00:35:01.040 --> 00:35:02.770
Approaching 800 million yuan.

00:35:03.690 --> 00:35:06.410
It was largely thanks to He Zhang
turning himself in

00:35:06.410 --> 00:35:07.770
and becoming a prosecution witness

00:35:07.770 --> 00:35:09.970
that the case had a major breakthrough.

00:35:18.770 --> 00:35:19.970
What brings you here?

00:35:20.640 --> 00:35:21.410
I'm sorry.

00:35:30.640 --> 00:35:32.300
Why are you apologizing to me?

00:35:34.040 --> 00:35:34.960
Because...

00:35:38.520 --> 00:35:39.980
I don't want to lose to you.

00:35:47.430 --> 00:35:48.800
When I was at Wan's,

00:35:50.140 --> 00:35:52.070
I did many things that wronged you.

00:35:54.070 --> 00:35:56.800
But about Wan Shengbang
tampering with your car,

00:35:57.760 --> 00:35:58.890
I truly didn't know.

00:36:03.930 --> 00:36:04.660
Jin Zhao,

00:36:07.850 --> 00:36:09.310
if there's still a chance,

00:36:11.750 --> 00:36:14.010
I wish to challenge you fairly once more.

00:36:23.980 --> 00:36:25.510
I'm going to turn myself in.

00:36:36.290 --> 00:36:37.430
He Zhang provided information

00:36:37.430 --> 00:36:40.490
on the trading methods between
Wan's and the Alliance.

00:36:44.750 --> 00:36:47.370
The Navy Headquarters and
the Anti-Smuggling Bureau joined forces,

00:36:47.370 --> 00:36:49.810
and with police departments
cooperating nationwide,

00:36:49.810 --> 00:36:51.810
we've arrested everyone involved.

